<p>Reality is merely an illusion, it’s all about perspective. Change your reality,
 experience a whole new world with virtual reality. Live in your own world, play your own game.<br><br>
Can’t afford a trip through space or a superfast rollercoaster ride? Take a digital trip in virtual reality! <br><br>
This workshop includes Basics of 3D modelling, import and integration into Unity engine, using the GVR plugin in Unity and exporting the game into your Android device. This workshop is concluded by installing these games into smartphones and playing thereafter.
